.TH smi-gintra-location "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Gintra Command"
.SH NAME
smi-gintra-location \- Print the SMI Gintra directory location
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B smi-gintra-location
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B smi-gintra-location
prints the absolute path to the Gintra data directory, typically located within the SMI variable data directory.
.SH AUTHOR
.PP
Command written by Imre Tabur.
Documentation written by Junie.
.SH "REPORTING BUGS"
.PP
Report smi-gintra-location bugs to \fIinfo@setmy.info\fR
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.PP
.BR smi-var-location (1),
